  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quiver and Die is a medieval top down zombie shooter where you play as an archer in a zombie infested dark fantasy world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With beautiful, <i>hand drawn</i> art and <i>carefully hand crafted</i> levels, Quiver and Die aims to provide a <strong>fun</strong>, <strong>action-packed</strong> and <strong>visually stunning</strong> gameplay experience. Here’s what you can expect from the game:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Infinite Replay Value</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/3ec1e3b632a9ae5ac993ce35ca73ed47.poster.avif?t=1747924483\" width=800 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/3ec1e3b632a9ae5ac993ce35ca73ed47.webm?t=1747924483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/3ec1e3b632a9ae5ac993ce35ca73ed47.mp4?t=1747924483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight never ending waves of zombies in four unique, hand crafted locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build Your Arsenal</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/8bba27861948e2b20023362d3c852c52.poster.avif?t=1747924483\" width=800 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/8bba27861948e2b20023362d3c852c52.webm?t=1747924483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/8bba27861948e2b20023362d3c852c52.mp4?t=1747924483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect more arrows to help you fight and unlock powerful upgrades to become a zombie-killing machine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rescue Your Friend</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/e896d6c62b2ce6e34753011a2a73415a.poster.avif?t=1747924483\" width=800 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/e896d6c62b2ce6e34753011a2a73415a.webm?t=1747924483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/e896d6c62b2ce6e34753011a2a73415a.mp4?t=1747924483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight your way to the Castle, where your kidnapped friend is being held, and free him from the zombie’s putrid clutches.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>And much...</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/8649d1949e298196dd410e7c42567bf7.poster.avif?t=1747924483\" width=800 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/8649d1949e298196dd410e7c42567bf7.webm?t=1747924483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/8649d1949e298196dd410e7c42567bf7.mp4?t=1747924483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >           <strong>...MUCH...</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/a58e97ac73839d535b7dc441ecef2b2c.poster.avif?t=1747924483\" width=800 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/a58e97ac73839d535b7dc441ecef2b2c.webm?t=1747924483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/a58e97ac73839d535b7dc441ecef2b2c.mp4?t=1747924483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                              <strong>...MORE!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/7edbff97f5c32767f61adfe485f8cf35.poster.avif?t=1747924483\" width=800 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/7edbff97f5c32767f61adfe485f8cf35.webm?t=1747924483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/7edbff97f5c32767f61adfe485f8cf35.mp4?t=1747924483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quiver and Die is a medieval top down zombie shooter where you play as an archer in a zombie infested dark fantasy world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With beautiful, <i>hand drawn</i> art and <i>carefully hand crafted</i> levels, Quiver and Die aims to provide a <strong>fun</strong>, <strong>action-packed</strong> and <strong>visually stunning</strong> gameplay experience. Here’s what you can expect from the game:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Infinite Replay Value</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/3ec1e3b632a9ae5ac993ce35ca73ed47.poster.avif?t=1747924483\" width=800 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/3ec1e3b632a9ae5ac993ce35ca73ed47.webm?t=1747924483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/3ec1e3b632a9ae5ac993ce35ca73ed47.mp4?t=1747924483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight never ending waves of zombies in four unique, hand crafted locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build Your Arsenal</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/8bba27861948e2b20023362d3c852c52.poster.avif?t=1747924483\" width=800 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/extras/8bba27861948e2b20023362d3c852c52.webm?t=1747924483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655330/